      "title": "Wedding in Wonderland for @WillaK",
      "preview": "The save-the-dates are printed and on their way...",
      "contextTitle": "Wedding Planning",
      "progressPercent": 71,
      "progressTone": "support",
      "workspaceLabel": "Golden Events",
      "composerPlaceholder": "Type a message...",
      "participants": [
        {
          "initials": "DC",
          "name": "Daisy Chain",
          "role": "Wedding Planner (Golden Events)",
          "tone": "advisor"
        },
        {
          "initials": "WK",
          "name": "Willa Karciana",
          "role": "Client (Bride)",
          "tone": "client"
        }
      ],
      "messages": [
        {
          "initials": "WK",
          "author": "@WillaK",
          "sentAt": "Jan 6, 3:09 PM",
          "text": "Dear Miss Chain, I just got engaged to the love of my life, Rufus Jackson. I'm looking for an event planner with style to help me plan my wedding at The Gorgeous. I want my wedding to be one of a kind (the theme will be \"Wedding in Wonderland\"). Are you available in the coming months? I will need full-service.",
          "tone": "client",
          "isBot": ""
        },
        {
          "initials": "DC",
          "author": "@DaisyChain",
          "sentAt": "Jan 6, 3:45 PM",
          "text": "Hi Willa, thank you for your kind message and congrats on your engagement! I would love to help you plan your wedding. I really like the theme you've picked. Could you please fill out this short survey for me?",
          "tone": "advisor",
          "isBot": ""
        },
        {
          "initials": "DC",
          "author": "@DaisyChain",
          "sentAt": "Jan 6, 6:35 PM",
          "text": "Thanks, Willa! Now I have a better understanding of your thoughts and ideas. Here's a proposal that I put together for you.",
          "tone": "advisor",
          "isBot": ""
        },
        {
          "initials": "WK",
          "author": "@WillaK",
          "sentAt": "Jan 6, 9:49 PM",
          "text": "This is exactly what I had in mind! I knew you would be the perfect choice. So, just send over the contract for me to sign, then I will send you the deposit, and we can get started with the fun part!",
          "tone": "client",
          "isBot": ""
        },
        {
          "initials": "DC",
          "author": "@DaisyChain",
          "sentAt": "Jan 7, 9:40 AM",
          "text": "Fantastic! Here's the finalized contract for you to sign.",
          "tone": "advisor",
          "isBot": ""
        },
        {
          "initials": "",
          "author": "System",
          "sentAt": "Jan 7, 10:57 AM",
          "text": "Willa Karciana has signed the contract.",
          "tone": "bot",
          "isBot": "true"
        },
        {
          "initials": "",
          "author": "System",
          "sentAt": "Jan 7, 11:10 AM",
          "text": "Invoice sent to Willa Karciana. Waiting for payment…",
          "tone": "bot",
          "isBot": "true"
        },
        {
          "initials": "",
          "author": "System",
          "sentAt": "Jan 7, 2:01 PM",
          "text": "Willa Karciana has transferred $1,500 to your account. A Wedding Planning Board has been created for you.",
          "tone": "bot",
          "isBot": "true"
        },
        {
          "initials": "DC",
          "author": "@DaisyChain",
          "sentAt": "Jan 7, 2:27 PM",
          "text": "Thanks for the deposit, Willa! To get started, I've created a Wedding Planning Board for us, where we can stay organized and keep track of our progress.",
          "tone": "advisor",
          "isBot": ""
        },
        {
          "initials": "",
          "author": "System",
          "sentAt": "Jan 7, 2:37 PM",
          "text": "Willa Karciana has joined your Wedding Planning Board.",
          "tone": "bot",
          "isBot": "true"
        },
        {
          "initials": "",
          "author": "System",
          "sentAt": "Jul 20, 5:02 PM",
          "text": "Daisy has added a document to the Wedding Planning Board.",
          "tone": "bot",
          "isBot": "true"
        },
        {
          "initials": "DC",
          "author": "@DaisyChain",
          "sentAt": "Jul 20, 5:03 PM",
          "text": "I just received a quote from our second DJ (Funky Bob). He charges about $100 less than Jimmy Joe and their music repertoires seem to be pretty much the same. Let me know if you have a preference.",
          "tone": "advisor",
          "isBot": ""
        },
        {
          "initials": "",
          "author": "System",
          "sentAt": "Jul 21, 8:58 AM",
          "text": "Daisy has added a document to the Wedding Planning Board.",
          "tone": "bot",
          "isBot": "true"
        },
        {
          "initials": "DC",
          "author": "@DaisyChain",
          "sentAt": "Jul 21, 9:02 AM",
          "text": "The save-the-dates are printed and on their way. You should receive them in the coming days.",
          "tone": "advisor",
          "isBot": ""
        },
        {
          "initials": "WK",
          "author": "@WillaK",
          "sentAt": "Jul 21, 9:52 AM",
          "text": "Awesome, can't wait to see them! By the way, about the DJ: Rufus spoke to a friend who went to a wedding Jimmy Joe played at. She really loved the music. So, I think we should go with Jimmy, even if he's more expensive.",
          "tone": "client",
          "isBot": ""
        },
        {
          "initials": "DC",
          "author": "@DaisyChain",
          "sentAt": "Jul 21, 9:58 AM",
          "text": "Sounds good, I'll book Jimmy Joe right away.",
          "tone": "advisor",
          "isBot": ""
        },
        {
          "initials": "DC",
          "author": "@DaisyChain",
          "sentAt": "Jul 20, 7:00 PM",
          "text": "We'll need to choose a style for the remaining wedding stationery soon (for invitations, programs, menu cards, thank yous and favors). Let me know if you need any help!",
          "tone": "advisor",
          "isBot": ""
        },
        {
          "initials": "WK",
          "author": "@WillaK",
          "sentAt": "Jul 20, 4:12 PM",
          "text": "I'll browse a little bit and see what kind of design works for both Rufus and me. I'll let you know once we've found some styles we both like.",
          "tone": "client",
          "isBot": ""
        },
        {
          "initials": "DC",
          "author": "@DaisyChain",
          "sentAt": "Jan 7, 11:11 AM",
          "text": "Thank you for signing the contract. Here's the invoice for the deposit I will need in order to get started. I look forward to working with you to plan this beautiful wonderland wedding!",
          "tone": "advisor",
          "isBot": ""
        },
        {
          "initials": "WK",
          "author": "@WillaK",
          "sentAt": "Jul 20, 7:00 PM",
          "text": "Thanks for letting me know. I'll talk to Rufus and we'll make a decision tonight.",
          "tone": "client",
          "isBot": ""
        }
      ],
